skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ship sailed
des: How well do you know your other half? In this party game for friends or couples, players pair up, and Alexa quizzes each player on how well they know their partner. The partner judges the responses. (Note from creator: I hope you like this! I made this when I was bored and had nothing else to do on a Friday night! c: enjoy! -Lauren) This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
